          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Photofission yields for the nuclei 238U, 235U, 232Th,",
                " 209Bi, 197Au,  and  181Ta  in  the   photon   energy",
                " interval from 100 MeV to 5 GeV are measured by means",
                " of the glass setectors.  The measured results are in",
                " satisfactory agreement with the yields calculated on",
                " the basis  of  photomeson  fission  model.  In   the",
                " fission cross sections of U and Th besides the giant",
                " resonance there is a resonance at the photon  energy",
                " E ~  300  MeV corresponding to the resonances in the",
                " photon-nucleon interaction   cross   section.    The",
                " integral photofission cross sections are presented."
              ]
            }
          ],
